		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>You charge the enemy and gore it with your horns.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Encounter</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Standard Action</b><b> &#8226; </b><b>Melee</b> 1</p><p><b>Effect:</b> You charge and make the following attack in place of a melee basic attack. </p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Target:</b> One creature </p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Attack:</b> Strength + 4 vs. AC, Constitution + 4 vs. AC, or Dexterity + 4 vs. AC. </p><p>Increase the bonus to attack rolls to +6 at 11th level and +8 at 21st level. </p><p><b>Hit:</b> 1d6 + Strength modifier, Constitution modifier, or Dexterity modifier damage, and you knock the target prone. </p><p><b>Level 11:</b> 2d6 + Strength modifier, Constitution modifier, or Dexterity modifier damage. </p><p><b>Level 21:</b> 3d6 + Strength modifier, Constitution modifier, or Dexterity modifier damage. </p><p>Published in Player's Handbook 3, page(s) 10. </p>",
